:"2017-12-15T04:51:35.000Z","msg":"雞，最少伏"},{"pid":"5273e8e827dd82089680e84e1fe2c9b81cac3a96","tid":499631,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1eed81e55ce08afe66a46e4f431d860fa5f2a5b8","tid":499631,"uid":1539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:58:56.000Z","msg":"雞其實真係好難煮得差 雖然唔同雞肉質都係會有分別"},{"pid":"033ad947c765f252c4b09da1252fbba9aa71e98e","tid":499631,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最鐘意食牛，但最鐘意煮雞，貪易煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛唔易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔熟都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛排其實真係唔易 好多人都會煮得太熟"},{"pid":"238d5de8e19600a6d3261f4d9eef9342e046141d","tid":499631,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最鐘意食牛，但最鐘意煮雞，貪易煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n牛唔易咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔熟都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要煮得好食的話，雞最易<br />\n煮過頭牛就好難食，但雞仲有雞皮啲油頂住<br />\n而且雞肉色味都比較淡，上色上味都更易控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27cc73513f2e8f376d22fd43f7b362f5d981652","tid":499631,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:07:04.000Z","msg":"食雞嘅話 最鐘意其實真係唔係食肉<br />\n雞心同雞腎總係覺得好正 但食得多應該好快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf389a6d03726cb8ab6d2a58f1eb2088a9fafc8","tid":499631,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:26:06.000Z","msg":"牛，雞，羊<br />\n<br />\n豬要中式，例如燒肉，乳豬"},{"pid":"bc6c104037b128a313aa2bd0d218633c69f06797","tid":499631,"uid":2565